title: #92Noon Live from the Combine! Schefter / Zimmer / Florio / Shurmur / Caplan
description:
Nine-to-Noon is live from the NFL Draft Combine in Indianapolis!

Guests include ESPN's Adam Schefter, Vikings Head Coach Mike Zimmer, PFT's Mike Florio, Giants Head Coach Pat Shrumur, and Pro Football Insider Adam Caplan!
